# Vector (Clock) Log

To provide a synchronizable log.

> vlog init -f file
> # Appends new content for the participant
> vlog append -f file -i in.file -p participant
> echo "content" | vlog append -f file -p participant
> # syncs the contents of in.file to file, only file is modified.
> vlog sync -f file -i in.file
> # lists out the content of the log file
> vlog list -f file [--pretty]

